  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="24007623">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mooooogumuji/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2762157-222.jpg" alt="E l e n o r e" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24007623/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24007623/" class="">第118页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mooooogumuji/" class=" " title="E l e n o r e">E l e n o r e</a>
                (壮士断腕的潇洒)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24007623">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">欺骗一条狗比欺骗一个人更残酷，因为它根本不知道我们在谈论什么，只懂得通过语调和表情来判断。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-19 09:35</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                欺骗一条狗比欺骗一个人更残酷，因为它根本不知道我们在谈论什么，只懂得通过语调和表情来判断。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

